{"title":"外国谚语（美国）","authors":[],"dates":[{"year":1977,"month":12,"day":24}],"parts":[{"type":"paragraph","text":"外国谚语（美国）"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"＊狼虽掉牙，凶性不改。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"＊甜言蜜语，是魔鬼射向心脏的箭。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"＊豺狼朝圣不可信。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"＊恶人的恨虽可憎，恶人的爱更危险。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"＊口吐甜言蜜语，难使嘴巴变甜。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"＊有的人用说大话来掩饰恐惧。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"＊狐狸说教，意在偷鸡。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"＊思危才能居安。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"＊一人发财，万人破产。"}],"comments":[],"comment_pivots":[],"description":"","page_start":6,"page_end":6}